            <h2>How to Care and Clean Furniture for it to Last Long?</h2>
            <p>When it comes to furniture, there are a few key things you need to do to keep it looking its best. First, dust your furniture regularly with a soft, clean cloth. You can also use a vacuum with a soft brush attachment on low setting to remove any dust that’s hard to reach.</p>
            <p>Next, once or twice a month, you will want to give your furniture a more thorough cleaning. You can do this by mixing equal parts water and white vinegar in a spray bottle and lightly misting the surface of your furniture. Wipe it down with a clean, dry cloth afterwards.</p>
